							</div>
							<p>分布式应用</p>
						</div>
						<div class="item col-md-1 col-sm-2 col-lg-offset-half col-md-offset-half col-sm-offset-half col-xs-3 col-xxs-offset-0">
							<div class="btn-icon">
								<i></i>
							</div>
							<p>区块链</p>
						</div>
						<div class="item col-md-1 col-sm-2 col-lg-offset-half col-md-offset-half col-sm-offset-half col-xs-3 col-xxs-offset-0">
